The paper discusses the recent advancements in deep learning on mobile devices, including hardware architectures, algorithm optimizations, and applications in various industries. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.LG (Machine Learning), followed by cs.CV (Computer Vision) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The paper also covers mobile sensing modalities, which could fall under cs.AR (Augmented Reality) and cs.EM (Emerging Technologies).
